{"type": "article", "id": 7011, "title": "三星 Gear Circle 蓝牙耳机", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-03T07:55:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234244vdwRMupDmTSZeIWq.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"white-space:normal;\">三星的这款蓝牙耳机的有趣之处在于，两端的耳机可以通过内置的磁极吸在一起，摇身一变，变成一个项圈的模样。同时，它拥有蓝牙耳机的全部功能，与手机接通后可以打电话，听音乐等等。这款耳机有白色，黑色和蓝色三种颜色。耳机挂在脖子上不是什么新提法，但像三星做的这么好看的就没几个了。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234242EsQ3KYZz6V8vCmHp.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.60462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052342432hcz9FevN6ogsbAB.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.60462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n<br>\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}